It is cold today 
=======
Get ready for a chilly night as skies clear and lows dip into the 30s in the mountains, and upper 40s in the valleys. Sunshine returns for the start of the weekend. Highs warm back to the upper 60s on Saturday and mid 70s for Sunday. Next week starts off mild, highs near 80 on monday, before storms move in by the middle of the week bringing highs back down into the 60s. Kevin Eubank - KSL Weather 9.15.2017
